        <title>Spin-based magnetic detection of optically trapped single cell in microfluidic channel</title>
            <categories>physics.optics quant-ph</categories>
            <comments>Accepted manuscript. The final published version appeared in Chinese Physics B 34, 070704 (2025)</comments>
            <journal-ref>Chinese Physics B 34, 070704 (2025)</journal-ref>
